description: Premier unit at Dahlgren Hall. Newer construction of 18 homes in a premier South Boston neighborhood offering exceptional amenities. West side location just off Broadway's shopping and restaurants, ½ mile to the T and 1 mi to the Seaport, this penthouse corner 2 bed/2 bath home boasts city views, a common rooftop terrace and club room with 360-vistas of Boston’s skyline. This is simply the best roof deck in South Boston. 1 Deeded assigned garage parking space. This home has an open floor plan, luxury appointments and high end upgrades enhance the contemporary ambiance. Hardwood, marble and tile floors. Kitchen island, marble counters, wine cooler, Thermador appliances and pantry. En suite primary with huge walk-in closet, glass shower and double vanity. Off the kitchen features a lovely private Juliet balcony.  Sonos sound system, high ceilings and brilliantly sunlit rooms with over-sized windows. Custom lighting, window treatments, shelving. Large private basement storage unit  160 SF
